channel.description: Just tried to install FicsIt-Networks mod, the result was repeated crashes and crash reports. I disabled all installed mods and enabled them one at a time and the error returned as soon as I enabled FicsIt-Networks. has this happened to anyone else or is it just me. Any suggestions please?
